snippet.textDisplay: I JUST got an Oculus GO for Christmas and it is AMAZING; the visuals, the sound capabilities, and the immersive-ness. Up until now I've only used systems that had you insert your phone into the headset. The only complaint I can even make for this system is it's charging time. It can take SO long to charge and then only lasts a short amount of time after charging. But besides that, it is WORTH it. I started watching Markiplier through VR, his Affected series being my first Let's Play of his.
